articles.author: Emily Brown
articles.title: People are feeling déjà vu after seeing Ryan Gosling's reaction to Emma Stone's Critics Choice Award speech - UNILAD
articles.description: Emma Stone won the Critics Choice Award for movie actress of the year for her role in Poor Things
articles.content:
When the cameras cut to Ryan Gosling as his friend and former co-star Emma Stone won at the Critics Choice Awards, fans quickly became convinced they'd seen a similar scene play out before.
